import React from 'react';

export default function firebaseLogo() {
  return (
    <svg
      id="Layer_1"
      data-name="Layer 1"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      xmlnsXlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
      viewBox="0 0 51 51"
    >
      <defs>
        <linearGradient
          id="linear-gradient"
          x1="-173.85"
          y1="223.27"
          x2="-173.53"
          y2="223.04"
          gradientTransform="matrix(109.5, 0, 0, -150.04, 19042.75, 33508.33)"
          gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
        >
          <stop offset="0" stopColor="#fff" stopOpacity="0.1" />
          <stop offset="1" stopColor="#fff" stopOpacity="0" />
        </linearGradient>
        <mask id="mask" x="6.52" y="2.11" width="37.9" height="47.88" maskUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <g transform="translate(1 1)">
            <g id="mask-3">
              <path id="path-2" d="M0,0Z" fill="#fff" fillRule="evenodd" />
            </g>
          </g>
        </mask>
        <mask id="mask-2" x="0" y="0" width="50.97" height="50.79" maskUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <g transform="translate(1 1)">
            <g id="mask-3-2" data-name="mask-3">
              <path id="path-2-2" data-name="path-2" d="M0,0Z" fill="#fff" fillRule="evenodd" />
            </g>
          </g>
        </mask>
        <mask
          id="mask-3-3"
          x="8.49"
          y="2.11"
          width="33.98"
          height="46.56"
          maskUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
        >
          <g transform="translate(1 1)">
            <g id="mask-3-4" data-name="mask-3">
              <path id="path-2-3" data-name="path-2" d="M0,0Z" fill="#fff" fillRule="evenodd" />
            </g>
          </g>
        </mask>
      </defs>
      <g id="Page-1">
        <g id="styleguide">
          <g id="Group-16">
            <g id="Group-9">
              <g id="Group-26">
                <g id="logo_lockup_firebase_vertical" data-name="logo lockup firebase vertical">
                  <g id="_Group_" data-name=" Group ">
                    <g id="_Path_5" data-name=" Path 5">
                      <path
                        id="path-2-4"
                        data-name="path-2"
                        d="M0,0Z"
                        transform="translate(1 1)"
                        fill="url(#linear-gradient)"
                      />
                    </g>
                    <g mask="url(#mask)">
                      <g id="_Group_2" data-name=" Group 2">
                        <g id="_Group_3" data-name=" Group 3">
                          <path
                            id="_Path_"
                            data-name=" Path "
                            d="M0,0Z"
                            transform="translate(1 1)"
                            fill="#ffa000"
                          />
                          <g id="_Group_4" data-name=" Group 4">
                            <image
                              id="Bitmap"
                              width="87"
                              height="112"
                              transform="translate(7 11) scale(0.26)"
                              opacity="0.12"
                              xlinkHref="data:image/png;base64,"
                              style={{isolation:"isolate"}}
                            />
                            <polygon id="Shape" points="28 25 22 14 8 40 28 25" fill="#f57c00" />
                          </g>
                        </g>
                        <g id="_Group_5" data-name=" Group 5">
                          <image
                            id="_Image_"
                            data-name=" Image "
                            width="140"
                            height="155"
                            transform="translate(8 9) scale(0.26)"
                            opacity="0.2"
                            xlinkHref="data:image/png;base64,"
                            style={{isolation:"isolate"}}
                          />
                          <g id="_Group_6" data-name=" Group 6">
                            <path
                              id="_Path_2"
                              data-name=" Path 2"
                              d="M0,0Z"
                              transform="translate(1 1)"
                              fill="#ffca28"
                            />
                          </g>
                        </g>
                        <path
                          id="_Compound_Path_"
                          data-name=" Compound Path "
                          d="M0,0ZM0,0Z"
                          transform="translate(1 1)"
                          fill="#fff"
                          fill-opacity="0.2"
                        />
                        <path
                          id="_Path_3"
                          data-name=" Path 3"
                          d="M0,0Z"
                          transform="translate(1 1)"
                          fill="#a52714"
                          opacity="0.2"
                          style={{isolation:"isolate"}}
                        />
                      </g>
                    </g>
                    <g mask="url(#mask-2)">
                      <polygon
                        id="_Path_4"
                        data-name=" Path 4"
                        points="0 0 51 0 51 51 0 51 0 0"
                        fill="none"
                      />
                    </g>
                    <g mask="url(#mask-3-3)">
                      <path
                        id="_Path_5-2"
                        data-name=" Path 5"
                        d="M0,0Z"
                        transform="translate(1 1)"
                        fill="url(#linear-gradient)"
                      />
                    </g>
                  </g>
                </g>
              </g>
            </g>
          </g>
        </g>
      </g>
    </svg>
  )
}
